## Project Overview

AI Echo is an end-to-end Sentiment Analysis system built to analyze ChatGPT user reviews and classify them into Positive, Neutral, or Negative categories.

This project demonstrates complete NLP workflow including:

- Data Preprocessing & Text Cleaning
- Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
- Feature Engineering using TF-IDF
- Machine Learning Models:
  - Logistic Regression
  - Random Forest
  - Naive Bayes
  - Support Vector Machine (SVM)
- Deep Learning Model:
  - LSTM (Long Short-Term Memory)
- Model Evaluation using:
  - Accuracy
  - Precision
  - Recall
  - F1-Score
  - Confusion Matrix
- Streamlit Web Application Deployment

The system provides real-time sentiment prediction with color-based visualization for improved user experience.
